Author: python_kiss
Title: Jeff Bezos'(Amazon CEO) Video Lecture on User Experience

Author: Harj
Content:
i'd just like to say it's great to read actual thoughtful comments about YC companies for once. i'm fed up of reading pathetic comments on Techcrunch from people who were rejected by YC and still like to claim they are into the startup scene without having anything to show for it.

i hope to meet some more of you guys at startup school this month.

Author: Harj
Content: highly recommended to everyone who can to attend this event.  jessica has learnt ALOT from interviewing all these founders and she can relay the experiences fantastically well.
